                     Kidāna Māryām (ras Sǝbḥāt ʾAragāwi, Additio 1, and <locus target="#54ra">54ra</locus>, 61ra), his mother is Walatta Yoḥannǝs (Additio 1, and <locus target="#47ra">47ra</locus>, 51ra).</provenance>
